### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### List all answers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/answers

### Create answer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/answers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brain_part_id": 1,
  "phrase": "A remembered moment"
}

### Create answer for another brain part
POST http://localhost:8080/api/answers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brain_part_id": 2,
  "phrase": "Someone who mattered"
}

### Validation: invalid brain part ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/answers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brain_part_id": 0,
  "phrase": "This should fail"
}

### Validation: empty phrase
POST http://localhost:8080/api/answers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brain_part_id": 1,
  "phrase": ""
}

### Validation: phrase longer than 40 characters
POST http://localhost:8080/api/answers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brain_part_id": 1,
  "phrase": "This phrase contains more than forty characters"
}
